"{\"uid\": \"people.com-swimmer-torri-huske-celebrating-olympic-medals-taylor-swift-eras-tour-exclusive-8690767\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Huske is heading from Paris to Vienna, Austria, to see Taylor Swift perform  Julie Mazziotta is the Senior Sports Editor at PEOPLE, covering everything from the NFL to tennis to Simone Biles and Tom Brady.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 205, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998009091285, \"rank\": 1.9909102300800353e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 31, \"end\": 37, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vienna\", \"score\": 0.9999927095970812, \"rank\": 7.177176805528834e-06, \"text\": \"Vienna\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vienna\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vienna\"}, {\"begin\": 39, \"end\": 46, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"score\": 0.9975128356257034, \"rank\": 0.002489054381519677, \"text\": \"Austria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\"}, {\"begin\": 55, \"end\": 67, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Swift\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.406825957188572e-31, \"text\": \"Taylor Swift\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Swift\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Swift\"}, {\"begin\": 161, \"end\": 164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.9975852361531565, \"rank\": 0.001039065017790985, \"text\": \"NFL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\"}, {\"begin\": 178, \"end\": 190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 195, \"end\": 204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Brady\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2533652934549627e-28, \"text\": \"Tom Brady\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Brady\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Brady\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was previously an Associate Editor for the Health vertical for six years, and prior to joining PEOPLE worked at Health Magazine.\", \"from\": 206, \"to\": 338, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When not covering professional athletes, Julie spends her time as a (very) amateur athlete, training for marathons, long bike trips and hikes.\", \"from\": 339, \"to\": 481, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kristy Sparow/Getty Images  Torri Huske, you just won three gold medals, how are you going to celebrate?\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 511, \"end\": 522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Torri_Huske\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Torri Huske\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Torri_Huske\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Torri_Huske\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By going to theEras Tour, of course!\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 624, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team USA swimmer Huskeearned five total medalsduring the2024 Gamesand set two world records in the process - remarkable accomplishments that she tells PEOPLE she's \\\"super excited\\\" about.\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 626, \"end\": 634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9992891337099693, \"rank\": 0.0005282661462828549, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, Huske tied for the most medals earned these Olympics by a swimmer, but came out on top for total golds.\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This meet has gone better than I could have hoped,\\\" Huske, 21, says on Aug. 5 at Team USA House in Paris.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 1033, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1009, \"end\": 1017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9992891337099693, \"rank\": 0.0005282661462828549, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1018, \"end\": 1023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\", \"score\": 0.9801699959197036, \"rank\": 0.020231022950126208, \"text\": \"House\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\"}, {\"begin\": 1027, \"end\": 1032, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998009091285, \"rank\": 1.9909102300800353e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am just so happy that I got to represent Team USA.\\\"\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1088, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1078, \"end\": 1086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9992891337099693, \"rank\": 0.0005282661462828549, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Huske hopes her accomplishments - amongst a setting of female athletes dominating in the victory count for Team USA - \\\"gets people to pay more attention to women's sports.\\\"\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1197, \"end\": 1205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9992891337099693, \"rank\": 0.0005282661462828549, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think that there is a bigger movement now where people are starting to pay attention more, and I think that's so awesome,\\\" she tells PEOPLE.\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1407, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Caitlin Clarkhas done so much for that, and I think she's so cool.\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1409, \"end\": 1416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Thomas\", \"score\": 0.9901928077955264, \"rank\": 0.009728927700105597, \"text\": \"Caitlin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Thomas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So hopefully I can also play a little part of that.\\\"\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Huske soon will transition focus back to her collegiate career at Stanford University.\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1616, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1596, \"end\": 1615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_University\", \"score\": 0.8975897041557113, \"rank\": 0.11398435230415441, \"text\": \"Stanford University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_University\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"First, though, she's going to have a little fun.\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1665, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am going to seeTaylor [Swift]in [Vienna,] Austria on [Aug.] 10th, which I am super excited about,\\\" Huske says.\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1780, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Huske waited until she made the U.S. Olympic team in late June, and then bought the Eras Tour tickets, she clarifies.\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1899, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But in the back of my mind I was always like, 'Oh, well if I am in Europe already, I have not seen her yet.\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 2008, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have to see her,' \\\" she says.\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2040, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So it was kind of in the back of my mind for a really long time.\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2106, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been wanting to see her for literally so long.\\\"\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2161, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And Huske does not resist the opportunity to get the music star a little shout-out.\", \"from\": 2163, \"to\": 2246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Michael Tran / AFP) (Photo by MICHAEL TRAN/AFP via Getty  \\\"Hi Taylor,\\\" she says.\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2263, \"end\": 2266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.999999685336938, \"rank\": 2.421503424578489e-07, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}, {\"begin\": 2286, \"end\": 2290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Parliament_Committee_on_Transport_and_Tourism\", \"score\": 0.9999999950634901, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"TRAN\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Parliament_Committee_on_Transport_and_Tourism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Parliament_Committee_on_Transport_and_Tourism\"}, {\"begin\": 2291, \"end\": 2294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.999999685336938, \"rank\": 2.421503424578489e-07, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am so excited to see you in concert and I am really excited also for when you eventually dropReputation.\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2436, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think I am a little bit delusional and I am just hoping that it happens at my concert, but regardless, I am so excited.\\\"\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2559, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From one record-breaker to another.\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2596, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To learn more about all the Olympic and Paralympic hopefuls, come topeople.comto check out ongoing coverage before, during and after the games.\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2741, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And sign up forGoing for Gold, our Olympics newsletter,to get the biggest stories from the Games delivered straight to your inbox.\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2872, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch the Paris Olympics and Paralympics, beginning July 26, on NBC and Peacock.\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 2953, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2937, \"end\": 2940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.987453215969902, \"rank\": 0.01194546313508609, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 2945, \"end\": 2952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pe